      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1>Shop</h1>
    <p class="coming-soon-subtitle">Loading...</p>
    <p class="coming-soon-description">
      STREETWATCH Shop will be partnering with a BMX shop in the near future. Making STREETWATCH shop your all-in-one street bmx platform.
    </p>
